OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start to Sunday but
OL,6,Flargely dry. Cloud breaking by the
OL,7,Fafternoon to leave sunny or bright
OL,8,Fspells. Breezy and feeling cool with
OL,9,Ftemperatures below average for early
OL,10,Fto mid-May.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA bright evening to end
OL,13,FSunday, however cloud will build from
OL,14,Fthe north with showery outbreaks of
OL,15,Frain reaching the region by dawn.
OL,16,FChilly under the clearest skies.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
