OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FOutbreaks of patchy rain will
OL,6,Fsink south across the West Midlands
OL,7,Fduring Monday morning, clearing to
OL,8,Fsunny spells into the afternoon.
OL,9,FFeeling rather chilly for the time of
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,13,FRemaining changeable on Tuesday with
OL,14,Foutbreaks of patchy rain clearing
OL,15,Fsouth. Turning blustery with sunny
OL,16,Fspells and heavy showers both
OL,17,FWednesday and Thursday. Feeling
OL,18,Fchilly, with a risk of frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
